SUMMARY:Rising Innovators: Alexa Stone\, Vertical Video Journalist
DESCRIPTION:Join us to meet Alexa "Lex" Stone\, vertical video journalist
  at the KC Star! She was previously a content creator for ESPN where she 
 broke social engagement records before becoming a full-time social produc
 er. During our event\, she will be judging our Vertical Video contest to 
 pick the first place $50 winner!  Our vertical video contest is for any s
 tudent who wants to enter. Create and publish a news vertical on Instagra
 m Reels and tag @innovationrji. We'll share your video and put it on the 
 list for the judging and prizes!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us to meet Alexa "Lex" Stone\, ver
 tical video journalist at the KC Star! She was previously a content creat
 or for ESPN where she broke social engagement records before becoming a f
 ull-time social producer. During our event\, she will be judging our Vert
 ical Video contest to pick the first place $50 winner!</p><p>  Our vertic
 al video contest is for any student who wants to enter. Create and publis
 h a news vertical on Instagram Reels and tag @innovationrji. We'll share 
 your video and put it on the list for the judging and prizes!</p>
